Text:
As the torrent says, these are amateurs, and as such, the photo quality is very poor for at least half of them. 
Also, a good deal of these photo's don't even come close to cutting it for even "nonude" porn- they are decidedly bland, and would not be considered out of place on something like facebook.

Decent-ish quality for the good ones... the few of them that there are, not really worth the time it takes to sift through them though.

This torrent sucks ass! 

As "Serianas" says:  not really worth the time it takes to sift through them...
